Package sample

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HealthState
    Our healt state interface
    IndividualFactory
    Factory interface for our factories
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CollisionState
    This state is represent Individual is in contact with other individual In move it waits for given time.
    Controller
    Controller class for fxml It holds a simulator object and call its fuctions to do everything When start button pressed it creates a thread and runs run(gameloop) funciton in simulator
    DeadState
    Dead state has an empty move and draw function so dead individual cant move or draw itself
    HealtyIndividualFactory
    Concrete Factory for building Healty Individual one by one or bulkly
    HealtyState
    Initial State for most of the individuals most of the time
    Hospital
    Hospital class for keeping the count of a hospital
    HospitalizedState
    This state waits for 10 secs and change its state via Mediator
    Individual
    Our backbone individual class Its our content for state pattern.
    InfectedIndividualFactory
    Concrete Factory for building Infected Individual one by one or bulkly
    InfectedState
    Concrete Healt State This is our infected state When every time a individual in this state moves its reduces its lifetime.
    Main
    Main FX class Starts our application
    Mediator
    Our mediator class It will do collide and hospitalize works
    Simulator
    It our simulator class Basically backend Server for our App It has list of individuals and all things about it It has our gameloop.
